#Iago_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.622981635104574,202,"I never did Offend you in my life, never loved Cassio But with such general warranty of heaven As I might love.","I do love Cassio well and would do much To cure him of this evil -  But hark!"

#Iago_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.635663240853856,34,"Be thou assured, good Cassio, I will do All my abilities in thy behalf.","Cassio hath beaten thee, And thou, by that small hurt, hast cashiered Cassio."

#Iago_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.654746611469159,6,"And so much duty as my mother showed To you, preferring you before her father, So much I challenge that I may profess Due to the Moor my lord.","It seems not meet nor wholesome to my place To be producted, as if I stay I shall, Against the Moor."

#Iago_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.655545010779584,75,"I will not leave him now till Cassio Be called to him.","Although 'tis fit that Cassio have his place -  For sure he fills it up with great ability -  Yet, if you please to hold him off awhile, You shall by that perceive him and his means."
#Iago_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.655937888378896,97,"How now, good Cassio, what's the news with you?","One of this kind is Cassio."
#Iago_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.65670406658919,89,"Pray you, let Cassio be received again.","One of this kind is Cassio."

#Iago_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.676888608327681,9,"That I love the Moor to live with him My downright violence and storm of fortunes May trumpet to the world.","Now, sir, be judge yourself Whether I in any just term am affined To love the Moor."
#Iago_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.688628063656603,82,"I' faith, is 't true?","I' faith, I fear it has."
#Iago_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.69652052420847,111,"I will go seek him.","I will go meet him."
#Iago_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.724131684834254,91,"I pray, talk me of Cassio.","One of this kind is Cassio."
#Othello_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.619007483784404,79,"I cannot speak of this.","I cannot speak enough of this content."
#Othello_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.622407578865463,200,"Then Lord have mercy on me!","I cry you mercy, then."
#Othello_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.626718184096213,89,"Pray you, let Cassio be received again.","Within these three days let me hear thee say That Cassio's not alive."
#Othello_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.647544366657568,75,"I will not leave him now till Cassio Be called to him.","Within these three days let me hear thee say That Cassio's not alive."
#Othello_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.650479814232743,202,"I never did Offend you in my life, never loved Cassio But with such general warranty of heaven As I might love.","Cassio shall have my place."

#Othello_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.652507947164694,34,"Be thou assured, good Cassio, I will do All my abilities in thy behalf.","I know, Iago, Thy honesty and love doth mince this matter, Making it light to Cassio."
#Othello_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.658663832078399,97,"How now, good Cassio, what's the news with you?","Within these three days let me hear thee say That Cassio's not alive."

#Othello_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.663507557759243,8,"Most gracious duke, To my unfolding lend your prosperous ear And let me find a charter in your voice T' assist my simpleness.","How may the Duke be therewith satisfied, Whose messengers are here about my side, Upon some present business of the state, To bring me to him?"
#Othello_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.672133456558435,91,"I pray, talk me of Cassio.","Within these three days let me hear thee say That Cassio's not alive."
#Othello_Oth,"#Desdemona_Oth",0.720222373929665,33,"What is the matter, dear?","What is the matter here?"
